        "KING_IN_SQUARE", Piece.Color.BLACK,
        "Defending king is within the pawn's promotion square and the attacking king cannot assist — with the move, the king intercepts the pawn before it queens. (de la Villa, Ending 1, p.27)",
        1, "de la Villa, Ending 1, p.27"
    ));
end

